<b>Ages of the Freedom Fighters</b>
<p><font color=red>As of what year were all the Sonic cast the age they are now? And in your  profiles can you include Ashura the Hedgehog? Please? </font>
<p>First, to clarify, here are the ages of the major Freedom Fighters:<BR> Sonic: 16<BR> Tails: 10<BR> Sally: 15<BR> Bunnie: 14<BR> Antoine: 18<BR> Amy Rose: 10 (Or now, 12)<P>  These ages are correct as of the Mobian year 3235.<P>  As far as Ashura goes, just talked with Vector and he says maybe. He's organizing a script, and it depends on how it goes. But thanks for pointing that one out. 
 - Brian Sapinski
