<p><table width=100% border=1 cellspacing=0 bordercolorlight=blue bordercolordark=23238E>
<tr><td bgcolor=000000><font face="Franklin Gothic Medium, Verdana" size=-1>
<b>Sonic Eco-Themes</b>
<p><font color=red>hi I love your site. GREAT WORK! anyway I have a question I was recently reading an archie sonic the hedgehog comic issue #71 and it showed that sonic turned to super sonic, ultra sonic and solar sonic? then he could turn into polar sonic or eco sonic? who are all these sonics? could you please straighten out how sonic's evoluntions go? and how he gets to  become them?<br> thanks fan</font>
<p>Other than Super Sonic, all the others are just a bunch of Sonic forms made up for issue #71 of the Archie Sonic Comic.  Well, Ultra had appeared before, but not the others.  It seems that these multiple transformations are meant to be an explanation for Sonic's having green eyes.  The transformations apparentlly depend on the ecosystem in which Sonic is running.
 - Vector
</font></td></tr></table>

<p><table width=100% border=1 cellspacing=0 bordercolorlight=blue bordercolordark=23238E>
